              <div class="hero-module__text h4">
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To make ends meet, Maybelle works two jobs, both in health care for the elderly. She’s the single mom of Jaeyk, a 15-year-old high school freshman. School is closed and now Jaeyk is home alone for most of the day. Maybelle is asking to be released from her night job two hours early so she can spend more time with him. She worries that he won’t be motivated to do his school work and that he’ll feel anxious home alone during this crisis. Right now, her biggest role is assuring Jaeyk that they’re both doing the best, and together they can make it work. #WeGotThis<br></span></p>
